source(output(
		SOURCE_CODE_KEY as string,
		SOURCE_SYSTEM as string,
		TARGET_CODE as string,
		TARGET_DESCRIPTION as string,
		CODE_TYPE as string,
		CODE_TYPE_ID as double,
		CODE2 as string,
		OM_X_REF as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	format: 'parquet') ~> tcrossreference
Ppebtable select(mapColumn(
		pebpeaid,
		pebpever_siv = pebpever,
		pebisolan
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> pebtableselect
Ppebtable select(mapColumn(
		pebpeaid,
		pebpever_test = pebpever
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> pebtablemax
pebtablemax aggregate(groupBy(pebpeaid),
	pebpever = max(pebpever_test)) ~> MaxPebver
pebtableselect, MaxPebver join(pebtableselect@pebpeaid == MaxPebver@pebpeaid
	&& pebpever_siv == pebpever,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'none')~> pebtable
Pagatable select(mapColumn(
		agaagaid,
		agaiyear,
		agaagno,
		agaagname,
		agaoffice,
		agabusndiv,
		agabusnsec,
		agabusncla,
		agasource,
		agaorgins,
		agastdate,
		agaendate,
		agauwsign,
		agaausign,
		agaclmsign,
		agaisic,
		agaadjsign,
		agaeosign,
		agasitid,
		agaadjsign = agaordercode,
		againtnote,
		agadatest,
		agauat
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> agatable
Pagztable select(mapColumn(
		agzagzid,
		agzcefoty,
		agzcurrgrosepi,
		agzepicurr,
		agzextadjynsw,
		agzfagntno,
		agzgtepi,
		agznoofobjepi
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> agztable
agatable, agztable join(agaagaid == agzagzid,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'none')~> AgaAgz
AgaAgz, pebtable join(agasource == pebtableselect@pebpeaid,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'none')~> AgaPeb
